{"tid":2359423,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中国廢舊電池廠大爆炸1死20傷   天空炸出「蘑菇雲」！","createTime":"2021-01-09T01:53:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-10T05:07:08.000Z","uid":184679,"like":178,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":90,"replies":[{"pid":"3bb4187ff2e59d7363fbc1085e94dd57c5505fe6","tid":2359423,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T01:53:10.000Z","msg":"湖南長沙市一間廢舊電池廠7日晚間突然爆炸，現場火勢猛烈，天空更出現「蘑菇雲」，在遠方都可清楚看見。官方通報，事故造成1人死亡，20人受傷，目前都已在醫院救治。<br />\n<br />\n綜合陸媒報導，發生事故的工廠是湖南邦普迴圈科技有限公司的老工廠，7日晚間6時12分突然發生燃炸意外，造成1人死亡，並有6人重傷、14人輕傷，目前已無生命危險。<br />\n<br />\n從現場影片中可見，火勢相當猛烈，消防部門調派36台消防車288名指戰員到場。大陸生態環境部門監測結果，事故廠區周邊環境空氣品質正常，善後處理工作正在抓緊進行中。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，出事公司成立於2008年，是大陸目前最大的廢舊鋰電池回收和高端電池材料生產的公司。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5385/d5385616.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5385%2Fd5385616.jpg&h=a15b2bbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/amp/amp_news.php?news_id=1894764&amp;from=google.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Famp%2Famp_news.php%3Fnews_id%3D1894764%26from%3Dgoogle.com&d=M%2BQ4vsyFJ%2Bls%2BsYkNkBEXTKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=2c4d8b9b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/amp/amp_news.php?news_id=1894764&amp;from=google.com</a>"},{"pid":"0a2d706494dbb506d9e18d5274beb38cafe25a38","tid":2359423,"uid":367280,"like":67,"dislike":3,"score":64,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T01:53:35.000Z","msg":"敵軍人數-1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5de31b4a81fb4f364dfef74296f9687ea34c1bf","tid":2359423,"uid":367280,"like":75,"dislike":0,"score":75,"citedBy":10,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T01:54:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NqkhNy7hAHY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNqkhNy7hAHY&d=M%2BQ4vsyFJ%2Bls%2BsYkNkBEXTKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=d1cb371a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/NqkhNy7hAHY</a>"},{"pid":"